Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.69,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I meant for you to hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:54.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,If I don't forget, I'll come\nback and dig you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.90,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\NYou must not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.25,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa, is Kagome's\nstory true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.15,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.46,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,A ghost appeared from\ninside the well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,and kidnapped Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.36,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the legend of our\nshrine goes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.83,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is something in the\N"bone-devouring well"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that takes the corpses of\nevil spirits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and makes them disappear\nsomewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:37.04,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if this "somewhere"is in\nthe time dimension...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.65,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, we must do something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:50.95,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,With written oracles to\nward off evil spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,and seal off the entry\nto the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.86,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The well will never\nbe opened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.48,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistaking the smell\nof that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.61,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Her clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:20.55,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! She really did\ngo home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:23.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.90,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmmm... Home sweet home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.40,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like it never happened...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.63,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I was in another age\nand another time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.01,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must combine your powers\nwith Inuyasha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gather the fragments of\nthe Sacred Jewel and restore it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.32,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear... The Sacred Jewel\nis in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.70,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That Yura with the inverted hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.13,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.67,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,She must've been after\nthe Jewel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet Inuyasha would\nbe so angry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.18,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,if he learned that the fragment\nwas stolen from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.58,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about you!?\NI prefer to go it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.62,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.05,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha can manage\nwithout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.55,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, I'll forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.73,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, I can never return\nto that world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:40.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, Yuka is on the phone.\NAnd it's also dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.40,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:45.24,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.07,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Will the seals on the well\never come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:48.90,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.07,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Each seal contains powerful words\nof magic that can't be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.48,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of evil\nspirit, it will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.58,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a hot pot for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:02.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,- So you can rest assured, Kagome.\N- Hot pot! Hot pot! Hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.25,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,She's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.26,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's such a glorious age!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.56,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.87,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh... Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.21,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Who said you can go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You... Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The well! Where else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.95,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The well? But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.02,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.65,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Those oracles have been used\nof this shrine since ancient times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.72,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,and cannot fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.56,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Oracle? You mean, this\nflimsy piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.66,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:41.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.53,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.39,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Wa... wait! I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:46.70,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:47.96,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:48.80,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.56,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Your ears... Are they real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme try, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:57.34,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom, this is no time for that...\NAlthough I did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,A strand of hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:03.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.75,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.05,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome... There's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:14.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:15.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.46,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only I can see it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.29,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,But being able to "see"\nisn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yura's manipulating strand!\NNo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.04,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,More strands... are coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.38,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That old crone was right.\NYou have the vision at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.62,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You brought something awful\nwith you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.39,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.22,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.40,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.16,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here... I must stop it right here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.07,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! In front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.61,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,- Open up, Kagome!\N- Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.35,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It gathers together again,\neven when it's cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.65,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.86,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! That's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.83,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The main strand that's\ncontrolling everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:32.73,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's this one!\NCut this strand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.80,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,This? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.61,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.88,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There's only one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.62,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.19,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.81,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strange...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.34,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Yura was after the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.81,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}she already accomplished\nher goal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:14.20,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could she actually be\nafter me and Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let's return!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:21.45,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow... That was a quick\nchange of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.29,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.36,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.82,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I stay here, Gramps,\NMom and even Sota...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.29,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be in terrible danger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.40,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,This was woven with the fur\nof the Fire Rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's much stronger than\nan ordinary armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.87,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Th... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:39.70,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, 'cuz...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.24,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You look like you have\nreally weird skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.57,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the weird one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.61,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, whatever.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.71,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.82,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,They should be returning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.39,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, I'll give them\na big reception...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Inuysha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.73,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is my sister Kikyo's\nreincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:19.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,However, she isn't aware yet\nof the scope of her powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.24,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,She needs your help\nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:26.21,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out! There's hair all\nover the well, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.88,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying that this Yura with\nthe combed Hair is after us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.76,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Look, she took the Sacred\NJewel fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.29,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,yet she still comes after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.30,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it! Did you say she\ntook it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.50,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see several glowing\nstrands of hair there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.20,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There's the main strand that's\nbeen bewitching the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.78,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That means if we follow\nthe main strand, we'll find Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.54,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:51.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:54.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no time to\nstand around and quarrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:58.61,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You need Kagome and\NKagome needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you must get through this\ndifficulty together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.30,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,A bonfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.13,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Their heads are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.14,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,They're fallen warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.81,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,They must've gotten tangled\nin the hair strands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.21,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Such bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop looking so depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:33.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,And don't start whining about\nwanting to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.58,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I... thought I'd borrow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must destroy Yura quickly\nor many innocent people will die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.37,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrows you shoot\nprobably won't hit their targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.04,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,How rude! If I practice, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.27,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.27,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,From now on! Just watch me!\NI'm going to improve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.45,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.78,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's hopeless, but\NI gotta admit, she's gutsy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The main lines are gathering.\NShe's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.69,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,From the left!\NThe right, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.63,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Too many! Use your instincts\nto evade them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.57,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Whhaa...?! What a useless woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.84,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you came to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.71,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:32.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.07,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The rear, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:42.58,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,A giant sphere of hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.46,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Yura's hiding place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... such a fine prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.47,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Inuyasha, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.44,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Yura?\NHow do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.78,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard the gossip in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.71,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That a half-demon named\NInuyasha is serving...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.78,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,the reincarnation of a\nshrine maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.05,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,and helping her to protect\nfor the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.22,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Me? Serving that\nbrainless girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.32,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:20.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... Well, both of you\nare brainless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.06,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Turning the Sacred Jewel\ninto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.57,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the Jewel fragment\nshe stole from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll deal with\nyou two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.87,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,and go look for the\nother fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.54,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Deal with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:40.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who'll rue\nthe day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.55,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,you appeared before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The same tactic over and\nover again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:12:59.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.03,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Such pretty hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,But you haven't taken\ncare of it, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.47,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,So many split ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.40,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, I'll shred you\nto pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, I'll shred you\nto pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.65,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Release Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I won't miss\nthis time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The woman who disappeared\nfrom the well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Release Inuyasha, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You two must be\nquite chummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.26,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Forget me\nand get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:20.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that pretty, but I think\NI'll take her hair, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.71,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,"Not that pretty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:29.55,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I condition my hair everyday!\NStop being so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.39,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.24,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,No! All my victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.41,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The heads of those\nfallen warriors we saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.32,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Your head will soon\noccupy a place there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.28,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,All this fine silver-colored hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.25,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't wait to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.76,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Before that, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.03,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You there! Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You scare me, so die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.20,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you like\nmy demon fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.70,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll feel the heat all the way\nto your bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.44,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,He... help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:25.98,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.44,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're being punished\nfor messing with my nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.31,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.38,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman...\nshe'll be left with no bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.65,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.28,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sad? Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.66,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you'll be joining her\nin no time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.62,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.80,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.46,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blades of blood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:52.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The strands are loosening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:56.58,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,My hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.81,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you can't control\nyour strands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:02.48,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You should treat ladies\nmore gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,People will laugh at\nyou, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Playtime's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:29.04,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn! I almost had your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.41,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.66,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just a half-demon\nwith half the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.90,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Poor little thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.37,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanted this in order to become\na full-fledged demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.18,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred... Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.91,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.67,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to sever your head\nvery carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,so that blood won't\nstain those silver locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.08,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit your joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:21.42,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! That'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.36,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Thrusting your hand into\nthe breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.53,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,of a woman you've only\njust met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.50,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You... you...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.77,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't feel anything?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:37.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You stole my Jewel fragment,\ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.75,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that wasn't nice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is it?!\NWhere is Yura's weak spot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.43,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.37,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have looked away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You are becoming a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.88,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't bat an eyelid when you\nwere struck or hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:18.04,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, you seem awfully upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.31,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Something worrying you\nover there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:22.82,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:25.72,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something inside that\N...that red skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.33,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Red Skull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.76,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,My web of hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.50,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,If it hurts you, let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.51,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.78,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you?\NWhy don't you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.85,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that she mentions{\i0} it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.32,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when engulfed in flames...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.86,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because of this robe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.13,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an armor made from\nthe fur of the Fire Rat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.89,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's much stronger than\nordinary metal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:08.97,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.83,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem like an\nordinary mortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.66,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,How's this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.38,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,l... Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.75,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you faint on me!\NI can't be looking after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.12,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.11,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I am immortal, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.75,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! The strand coming\nout of this red skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.26,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's connected to Yura's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman... I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's Yura's true form...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,This red comb?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:52.94,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the Adornment Comb of\nthe Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.33,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It was used to comb the hair\nof the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.34,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,that's how it probably\ngot bewitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,In this day and age, an\nenchanted comb or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.64,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,is nothing to be surprised at.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.02,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... you're badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.35,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Because you let me wear your\NFire Rat armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:09.95,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.79,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,But the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.23,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.20,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it'll take to\naccumulate them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.80,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:25.93,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.53,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:30.00,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the first time you\nsaid my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:31.91,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.90,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you've decided to be\na bit nicer to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.28,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't get cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.92,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd be chums with a\ngirl like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.35,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! And who was it\nthat just saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:48.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Look... if it hurts, just\nspeak up and say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.56,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.09,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:57.26,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Join your powers and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:04.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,And hurry up and remember that\nyou buried me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:50.54,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,I was saved by the Fire Rat robe\nthanks to Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:53.98,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,That reminds me of a story of Princess\NKaguya from the Tale of Taketori.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:57.02,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,She didn't want to get married so she\ngave away the Fire Rat robe instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:59.99,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,So that robe was from\nthe demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.75,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,And now the phantom sword\NTetsusaiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:07.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Battle begins between two brothers\nfor the possession of the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:12.10,Inuyasha,Comment,0,0,0,,Next time, Inuyasha "Aristocratic\NAssassin, Sesshomaru" See you soon!
